    <description>An intelligent upgrade to the QBZ-101 shotgun system, featuring a high-capacity drum magazine design that significantly increases the volume of fire. Its new target analysis computer utilizes real-time threat assessment algorithms to automatically switch to the optimal secondary target after eliminating the current one, providing firing guidance.\n\nProjectiles fired from this weapon inflict significant stun and stagger effects on impacted targets.</description>
